<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200807/b2a5f15f1ae049369b585ea36896fc47.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">黄名芊《踏雪远行图》145x365cm</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200807/13c04173fb1a40de9d0557ff12d6a2dd.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">黄名芊《丝绸之路风光》68x136cm</span></img></p>
